{"_id":"sp001","name":"Mage Light","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/light.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a floating orb of light, about the size of your fist, that hovers near you.\nIt provides bright light in a 5-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet.\nIt lasts for one hour or until you dismiss it.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp002","name":"Mend","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/repair.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a single tear or break in an object (no larger than 1 foot in any dimension) and cause it to be seamlessly repaired.\nThis cannot restore magic to a broken magical item.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp003","name":"Prestidigitation","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/magic-swirl.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You perform a minor, harmless magical trick.\nYou can instantly clean or soil an object, chill or warm a small amount of non-living material, create a small, harmless sensory effect (like a shower of sparks, a puff of wind, or a faint musical note), or light/snuff out a small flame like a candle or torch.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp004","name":"Detect Magic","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/eye.svg","system":{"description":"<p>For up to 10 minutes, you can sense the presence of active magical effects within 30 feet of you.\nYou see a faint aura around any visible creature or object that is currently under the effect of a spell or possesses an active magical property.\nThis does not detect the innate magical potential of a creature.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp005","name":"Mage Armor","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a willing creature who isn't wearing armor, and a protective magical force surrounds it.\nThe target gains Damage Reduction 2. The spell ends if the target dons armor or if you dismiss it as an action.\nLasts for 8 hours.</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp006","name":"Floating Disc","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/circle.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a circular, horizontal plane of force, 3 feet in diameter, that floats 3 feet above the ground.\nIt can hold up to 500 pounds. It remains stationary unless you move more than 20 feet away from it, at which point it follows you.\nLasts for 1 hour. (Concentration)</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp007","name":"Arcane Lock","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/lock.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a door, chest, or other object that can be closed, and it becomes magically locked.\nA creature can use its action to make a Strength check to break it open (DC 15).\nYou can set a password that, when spoken, suppresses the spell for 1 minute.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp008","name":"See Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/eye.svg","system":{"description":"<p>For one hour, you can see invisible creatures and objects as if they were visible.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp009","name":"Dispel Magic","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/unholy-aura.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Choose one creature, object, or magical effect within range. You attempt to unravel the magic.\nThis is a competitive roll: you make a spellcasting ability check, and the GM rolls against you.\nThe GM's difficulty is based on the power of the effect you are trying to dispel.\nOn a success, the magical effect ends.</p>","cost":3,"tradition":"General"}}
{"_id":"sp010","name":"Spark","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You hurl a mote of fire at a creature or object.\nMake a ranged spell attack. On a hit, the target takes 1d4 fire damage.\nA flammable object hit by this spell ignites if it isn't being worn or carried.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp011","name":"Gust","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/wind.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a small blast of wind capable of pushing an object weighing up to 5 pounds up to 10 feet away from you.\nIt can also be used to flutter banners, rustle leaves, or snuff out small, unprotected flames.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp012","name":"Shape Water","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/water-drop.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can manipulate a 5-foot cube of water.\nYou can change its flow, form it into simple shapes, or cause it to freeze (though this doesn't do damage).</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp013","name":"Burning Hands","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","system":{"description":"<p>As an action, you cause a thin sheet of flames to erupt from your hands.\nEach creature in a 15-foot cone must make a Dexterity saving throw.\nA creature takes 2d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp014","name":"Fog Cloud","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/fog.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a 20-foot-radius sphere of fog centered on a point within range.\nYou can see through this fog as if it were not there.\nFor all other creatures, the sphere is heavily obscured. It lasts for up to 1 hour.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp015","name":"Ball Lightning","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a crackling sphere of electricity at a point you choose within 60 feet.\nThe sphere erupts in a 30-foot radius burst. Each creature in the area must make a Dexterity saving throw.\nA creature takes 3d6 lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp016","name":"Scorching Ray","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create three rays of fire and hurl them at targets within 60 feet.\nYou can hurl them at one target or several. Make a ranged spell attack for each ray.\nOn a hit, the target takes 2d6 fire damage.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp017","name":"Wall of Fire","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/fire-wall.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a wall of fire on a solid surface within 120 feet.\nThe wall can be up to 60 feet long, 20 feet high, and 1 foot thick.\nWhen the wall appears, each creature within its area must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking 5d8 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much on a successful one.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":4,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp018","name":"Wall of Ice","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/ice-wall.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a wall of ice on a solid surface within 120 feet.\nThe wall can be up to 60 feet long, 15 feet high, and 1 foot thick.\nEach 10-foot section of the wall has 30 HP and is vulnerable to fire damage.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":4,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp019","name":"Wall of Wind","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/wind-wall.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a wall of wind on a solid surface within 120 feet.\nThe wall can be up to 50 feet long, 15 feet high, and 1 foot thick.\nRanged weapon attacks that pass through the wall automatically miss.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":4,"tradition":"Elemental"}}
{"_id":"sp020","name":"Minor Illusion","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/sound.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a sound or an image of an object that lasts for 1 minute.\nThe sound can be as loud as a normal conversation.\nThe image must fit in a 5-foot cube and cannot create sensory effects other than sight.\nYou can use your action to move the image. Physical interaction with the image reveals it to be an illusion.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Conjuring"}}
{"_id":"sp021","name":"Unseen Servant","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/ghost.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You summon an invisible, mindless, shapeless force that performs simple tasks at your command.\nIt has a Strength of 2 and can perform tasks a human servant could do.\nIt lasts for 1 hour.</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Conjuring"}}
{"_id":"sp022","name":"Mirror Image","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/duality.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Three illusory duplicates of yourself appear in your space.\nUntil the spell ends, the duplicates move with you. Each time a creature targets you with an attack, roll a d20 to see if the attack targets one of your duplicates instead.\nA duplicate is destroyed if an attack hits it.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Conjuring"}}
{"_id":"sp023","name":"Magic Jump","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/parry.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space that you can see.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Conjuring"}}
{"_id":"sp024","name":"Summon Lesser Spirit","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/wolf-head.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You call forth a lesser spirit which takes the form of a beast (e.g., a wolf, an eagle).\nThe spirit is friendly to you and your companions and obeys your commands. It acts on its own turn.\nIt disappears after 1 hour, when it drops to 0 HP, or if you dismiss it.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":3,"tradition":"Conjuring"}}
{"_id":"sp025","name":"Message","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/whisper.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You point your finger toward a creature and whisper a message.\nThe target (and only the target) hears the message and can reply in a whisper that only you can hear.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Mental"}}
{"_id":"sp026","name":"Charm Person","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/love-mystery.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You attempt to charm a humanoid you can see.\nIf you or your companions are fighting it, the spell has no effect.\nOtherwise, it must make a Wisdom saving throw. If it fails, it is charmed by you for 1 hour or until you do anything harmful to it.</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Mental"}}
{"_id":"sp027","name":"Sleep","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/sleep.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You attempt to send creatures into a magical slumber.\nIn a 20-foot radius burst, all creatures must make a Constitution saving throw.\nThose who fail fall unconscious for 1 minute.</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Mental"}}
{"_id":"sp028","name":"Suggestion","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/brain.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You influence a creature you can see that can hear and understand you.\nYou suggest a course of activity, and on a failed Wisdom saving throw, the creature pursues the action to the best of its ability for up to 1 hour.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Mental"}}
{"_id":"sp029","name":"Hold","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Choose a living creature that you can see. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be paralyzed for up to 1 minute.\nAt the end of each of its turns, the target can make another Wisdom saving throw to end the effect.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Mental"}}
{"_id":"sp030","name":"Confusion","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You create a psychic blast in a 10-foot-radius sphere. On a failed Wisdom save, an affected target can't take reactions and attacks the nearest creature for 1 minute.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":4,"tradition":"Mental"}}
{"_id":"sp031","name":"Stabilize","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/heal.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a living creature that has 0 Hit Points.\nThe creature becomes stable, which means it doesn't have to make death saving throws.\nThis spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Life"}}
{"_id":"sp032","name":"Siphon Vigor","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/leech.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You make a melee spell attack against a creature.\nOn a hit, the target takes 1d4 necrotic damage, and you gain temporary Hit Points equal to the damage dealt.</p>","cost":0,"tradition":"Life"}}
{"_id":"sp033","name":"Cure Wounds","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/heal.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a living creature and restore 1d6 Hit Points.\nIf this spell is cast on an undead creature, it instead takes 1d6 damage.</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Life"}}
{"_id":"sp034","name":"Restoration","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/regeneration.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a creature and can end either one disease or one condition afflicting it.\nIf the affliction is non-magical, it is automatically cured. If it is magical in nature, you must succeed on a competitive spellcasting check against the effect's power to cure it.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Life"}}
{"_id":"sp035","name":"Life Link","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/link.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You touch a willing or unwilling creature, creating a bond between you.\nFor the duration, each turn you can choose to use your action to either siphon 1d3 hit points from a linked enemy to heal yourself, or take 1d3 damage to heal a linked ally for the same amount.\nThe spell lasts for 1 minute. (Concentration)</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Life"}}
{"_id":"sp036","name":"Vampiric Touch","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/leech.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Make a melee spell attack against a creature.\nOn a hit, the target takes 3d6 necrotic damage, and you regain Hit Points equal to half the amount of necrotic damage dealt.</p>","cost":3,"tradition":"Life"}}
{"_id":"sp037","name":"Spirit Sight","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/eye.svg","system":{"description":"<p>As an action, you can see into the spirit world for 1 minute.\nYou can see the emotional state of living creatures as colorful auras and perceive invisible spirits.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":1,"tradition":"Spirit-Touched"}}
{"_id":"sp038","name":"Whispers of the Past","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You spend 10 minutes and touch an object of great importance to a deceased individual to contact their lingering spirit.\nThis requires a Spirit-Touched skill check, with the DC set by the GM based on the time since death and the spirit's willingness to speak.</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Spirit-Touched"}}
{"_id":"sp039","name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/sound.svg","system":{"description":"<p>As an action, you allow a willing spirit to speak through you for 1 minute.\nThis may grant you knowledge you don't possess or allow you to speak a language you don't know, but it may also invite unwanted spiritual attention.\n(Concentration)</p>","cost":2,"tradition":"Spirit-Touched"}}
